1
00:00:11,030 --> 00:00:14,160
♫ When romance is too insignificant ♫

2
00:00:14,160 --> 00:00:21,640
♫ But I can't stop missing you, like a bad cold ♫

3
00:00:21,640 --> 00:00:28,300
♫ Drifting in a deserted island, where feelings have no reception ♫

4
00:00:28,300 --> 00:00:32,140
♫ Have you been well? ♫

5
00:00:32,140 --> 00:00:36,230
♫ Don't worry, I'll be fine ♫

6
00:00:36,230 --> 00:00:39,390
♫ Don't worry, I can't fall asleep ♫

7
00:00:39,390 --> 00:00:46,860
♫ Don't worry, I can't get used to this lonely world ♫

8
00:00:46,860 --> 00:00:53,620
♫ Hitting the pause button, leaving your side ♫

9
00:00:53,620 --> 00:01:00,770
♫ Letting the memories migrate to that day of happiness ♫

10
00:01:00,770 --> 00:01:07,080
♫ I'm trying hard to smile as I say goodbye to you ♫

11
00:01:07,080 --> 00:01:12,950
♫ I recall and long for the happiness you want, I can make it happen ♫

12
00:01:12,950 --> 00:01:16,100
♫ Can't hold back the tears, leading to regret ♫

13
00:01:16,100 --> 00:01:22,060
♫ Losing you whom I love, heartbreak is inevitable ♫

14
00:01:22,060 --> 00:01:28,580
♫ I choose to bid farewell with a smile ♫

15
00:01:28,580 --> 00:01:31,260
[Lost Romance]

16
00:01:31,260 --> 00:01:35,260
As soon as Situ Moran appeared, Boss dreamt about He Tianxing.

17
00:01:35,260 --> 00:01:37,320
I can't help He Tianxing in the real world.

18
00:01:37,320 --> 00:01:41,540
But here, I absolutely won't let Situ Moran hurt Boss.

19
00:01:41,540 --> 00:01:43,250
Marketing Department's Zheng Xiao'en

20
00:01:43,250 --> 00:01:46,700
defeated the tenth consecutive winner, Accounting Department's reimbursement cashier,

21
00:01:46,700 --> 00:01:49,960
and become our Royal Group's champion for being the most loathsome person.

22
00:01:49,960 --> 00:01:53,130
Xiao'en just got locked in the bathroom and had water splashed all over her.

23
00:01:53,130 --> 00:01:56,720
You knew it was me, yet you still came to save me?

24
00:01:56,720 --> 00:02:03,340
I, Zheng Xiao'en, have successfully become the overbearing CEO's little rose.

25
00:02:03,340 --> 00:02:05,650
I thought you simply wanted to help me.

26
00:02:05,650 --> 00:02:08,040
I never thought you would bring the CEO to the hospital

27
00:02:08,040 --> 00:02:10,550
and let him know that my family owed money.

28
00:02:10,550 --> 00:02:13,700
In front of him, I don't even have a bit of pride anymore.

29
00:02:13,700 --> 00:02:18,250
Scheming woman seduces the CSO into a love rendezvous in the middle of the night.

30
00:02:18,250 --> 00:02:20,380
Why would someone take these photos?

31
00:02:20,380 --> 00:02:23,830
It means there's someone in the company who harbors malicious intentions toward Xiao'en.

32
00:02:23,830 --> 00:02:26,470
Shouldn't you be paying more attention to her safety?

33
00:02:26,470 --> 00:02:31,960
More importantly, what plans do you have for Zheng Xiao'en?

34
00:02:42,610 --> 00:02:50,060
[Lost Romance]

35
00:02:50,060 --> 00:02:52,730
[Chapter Twelve]

36
00:03:02,030 --> 00:03:03,430
Why did you come back?

37
00:03:03,430 --> 00:03:07,160
If I didn't come, would I be able to clearly see your two-faced true colors?

38
00:03:07,160 --> 00:03:08,980
You're the most shameless person I've ever met.

39
00:03:08,980 --> 00:03:12,880
You support me on the surface, but you seduce him behind my back.

40
00:03:12,880 --> 00:03:16,750
You purposely sent the others away so that you could take a photo with the CEO, right?

41
00:03:16,750 --> 00:03:22,030
I really wasn't supporting you on the surface and pulling dirty tricks behind your back. I was—

42
00:03:22,030 --> 00:03:23,490
I don't need your explanation.

43
00:03:23,490 --> 00:03:28,500
I just want you to leave the CEO, leave the CSO, leave the company, and leave the further, the better!

44
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:50,270
What's going on?

45
00:03:54,640 --> 00:03:58,380
Zheng Xiao'en... Zheng Xiao'en hit me.

46
00:03:58,380 --> 00:04:01,310
- Why did you hit her?
- What’s going on now?

47
00:04:01,310 --> 00:04:03,910
Zheng Xiao'en hit someone?

48
00:04:06,870 --> 00:04:10,110
It's okay. First, explain what happened clearly.

49
00:04:11,140 --> 00:04:12,900
I also don’t know what happened.

50
00:04:12,900 --> 00:04:15,290
Xiao’en said she has been busy for a couple of days.

51
00:04:15,290 --> 00:04:19,250
Since no one was watching anyway, she asked me to come over and tidy up.

52
00:04:19,250 --> 00:04:23,020
After I came, Xiao'en got mad at me and asked why I was so slow.

53
00:04:23,020 --> 00:04:25,730
I wanted to explain, but Xiao'en wouldn't listen.

54
00:04:25,730 --> 00:04:27,200
She forcefully pushed me.

55
00:04:27,200 --> 00:04:29,930
- She only knows how to do superficial work.
- What goes around comes around.

56
00:04:29,930 --> 00:04:32,740
- I could see that she's so fake.
- She's so two-faced.

57
00:04:32,740 --> 00:04:36,100
She just wants to show off in front of senior executives.

58
00:04:36,100 --> 00:04:38,120
Xiao'en isn't that type of person.

59
00:04:41,760 --> 00:04:44,450
Is there some sort of misunderstanding?

60
00:04:44,450 --> 00:04:48,210
If the CEO says it's a misunderstanding, then I guess it's a misunderstanding.

61
00:04:48,210 --> 00:04:50,440
No matter what the situation was, is it right to hit people?

62
00:04:50,440 --> 00:04:52,070
You’ve become so arrogant now.

63
00:04:52,070 --> 00:04:54,220
Hey! You're all so weird.

64
00:04:54,220 --> 00:04:56,170
In the past, did you ever support Chuchu like this?

65
00:04:56,170 --> 00:04:58,920
And did you personally see what happened?

66
00:05:02,080 --> 00:05:04,010
Is your arm okay?

67
00:05:08,630 --> 00:05:13,600
- It hurts.
- Apologize! Apologize! Apologize!

68
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:16,480
Hurry and apologize!

69
00:05:25,310 --> 00:05:28,120
I think this issue isn't a big deal.

70
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:33,830
Xiao'en, why don't you apologize to Chuchu and we will drop this issue?

71
00:05:47,570 --> 00:05:50,000
You want me to apologize.

72
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:54,010
You believe her?

73
00:05:55,430 --> 00:05:56,720
That's not what I mean.

74
00:05:56,720 --> 00:05:59,170
Shouldn't the person who hit someone apologize?

75
00:05:59,170 --> 00:06:01,380
Now that you have the CEO looking out for you, are you just acting arrogantly?

76
00:06:01,380 --> 00:06:06,010
- Hurry and apologize!
- Apologize! Hurry and apologize!

77
00:06:19,350 --> 00:06:21,270
Xiao'en.

78
00:06:46,720 --> 00:06:49,020
I'm sorry!

79
00:06:49,610 --> 00:06:51,920
- Xiao'en!
- I'll go!

80
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:54,620
- She has the CEO as her support.
- She’s not even putting on an act anymore.

81
00:06:54,620 --> 00:06:55,900
She’s publicly hitting people.

82
00:06:55,900 --> 00:06:57,250
The CEO even ran out in a hurry.

83
00:06:57,250 --> 00:06:58,970
Is he afraid that she will be hit by a car?

84
00:06:58,970 --> 00:07:01,030
Hey! Watch what you say!

85
00:07:01,030 --> 00:07:02,210
Did I say something wrong?

86
00:07:02,210 --> 00:07:03,630
People like Zheng Xiao’en actually has guards.

87
00:07:03,630 --> 00:07:05,590
You’re the one who will be hit by a car! Your whole family will be hit by cars!

88
00:07:05,590 --> 00:07:09,890
Enough! Enough! It’s dangerous to anger this mass of people. Tolerate them first.

89
00:07:09,890 --> 00:07:11,820
There must be some sort of misunderstanding.

90
00:07:11,820 --> 00:07:15,470
Everyone calm down first. Don’t be so angry.

91
00:07:16,820 --> 00:07:19,240
I really don’t know what I did wrong.

92
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:21,700
Why did Xiao’en get so angry?

93
00:07:21,700 --> 00:07:24,200
- She’s really gone too far.
- Are you all right?

94
00:07:24,200 --> 00:07:26,970
Are you okay?

95
00:07:38,080 --> 00:07:40,190
Let's talk.

96
00:07:41,560 --> 00:07:44,990
What happened? Why did you hit Chuchu?

97
00:07:48,230 --> 00:07:52,970
Is it because I liked her before, so you're jealous?

98
00:07:56,620 --> 00:08:01,300
Being jealous is normal, but hitting someone isn't cute.

99
00:08:01,300 --> 00:08:04,050
Shouldn't you apologize?

100
00:08:12,010 --> 00:08:17,670
You think I hit her because I'm jealous?

101
00:08:21,970 --> 00:08:26,990
So in your mind, you actually see me as a really narrow-minded person.

102
00:08:26,990 --> 00:08:33,460
Because you're not narrow-minded, I wanted to ask you what happened.

103
00:08:36,340 --> 00:08:39,800
You want to know? Fine, I'll tell you.

104
00:08:39,800 --> 00:08:43,110
Because she's trying to mess with me. She's being shady.

105
00:08:43,880 --> 00:08:45,900
There are many people who want to mess with me.

106
00:08:45,900 --> 00:08:48,890
Every day at work, I have to fight monsters to level up.

107
00:08:48,890 --> 00:08:50,960
Do you think I'm foolish?

108
00:08:52,910 --> 00:08:54,980
Not at all.

109
00:08:54,980 --> 00:08:58,700
Then why am I being stabbed in the back?

110
00:08:58,700 --> 00:09:02,260
It's because I didn't guard against her.

111
00:09:02,260 --> 00:09:05,570
Even though we are rivals in love,

112
00:09:05,570 --> 00:09:08,970
I really gave it my all to help her.

113
00:09:10,510 --> 00:09:13,970
Anyone can mess with me, just not Chuchu!

114
00:09:15,770 --> 00:09:18,540
Some rules of a group are unreasonable.

115
00:09:18,540 --> 00:09:23,690
But in order to survive, you must at least have a basic understanding.

116
00:09:23,690 --> 00:09:27,900
Otherwise, one day you'll become the target.

117
00:09:27,900 --> 00:09:31,210
You won't even know how you died.

118
00:09:31,210 --> 00:09:32,620
Your dad's medical fees.

119
00:09:32,620 --> 00:09:35,100
Don't worry, I'll take care of the rest of the fees.

120
00:09:35,100 --> 00:09:36,940
Master, your drink is here.

121
00:09:36,940 --> 00:09:39,050
I'll make it taste good for you now.

122
00:09:39,050 --> 00:09:42,100
- Welcome home, master.
- Hi.

123
00:09:42,100 --> 00:09:44,030
Meow.

124
00:09:45,190 --> 00:09:50,570
If I didn’t slap her, I would've been so angry until my internal organs started hurting.

125
00:09:50,570 --> 00:09:53,580
So you didn't push her?

126
00:09:53,580 --> 00:09:55,560
I'm a person who is willing to take responsibility for what I do.

127
00:09:55,560 --> 00:09:58,040
If I didn't do it, I didn't.

128
00:09:59,800 --> 00:10:01,710
Then why did she lie?

129
00:10:01,710 --> 00:10:04,670
Go ask her. Don't ask me.

130
00:10:04,670 --> 00:10:08,950
Chuchu doesn't look like someone who would speak carelessly.

131
00:10:11,830 --> 00:10:15,550
She doesn’t look like it, but I do?

132
00:10:15,550 --> 00:10:17,550
That’s not what I meant.

133
00:10:17,550 --> 00:10:20,570
I just feel very shocked. Chuchu wasn’t like this before.

134
00:10:20,570 --> 00:10:23,020
I’m even more shocked than you are.

135
00:10:23,830 --> 00:10:26,320
Not only that, I feel very hurt.

136
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:34,610
What's even more frustrating is that you actually believed such a lousy dirty trick!

137
00:10:34,610 --> 00:10:36,180
All men are the same.

138
00:10:36,180 --> 00:10:39,550
When they see pretty girls, their IQ just goes offline.

139
00:10:39,550 --> 00:10:41,660
When did I ever do that?

140
00:10:42,380 --> 00:10:46,000
You want to say that about me, but aren't you the same?

141
00:10:47,160 --> 00:10:49,690
What did I do this time?

142
00:10:50,430 --> 00:10:51,890
Don’t tell me that you are going to bring up the past

143
00:10:51,890 --> 00:10:54,320
and raise the issue of me and Qingfeng again.

144
00:10:56,490 --> 00:10:58,230
The relationship between me and Supreme Master

145
00:10:58,230 --> 00:11:01,540
is pure, open, and dignified.

146
00:11:01,540 --> 00:11:03,220
It’s fine if you want to talk badly about me.

147
00:11:03,220 --> 00:11:06,440
Given your close relationship with him, doesn’t it hurt your conscience to question him?

148
00:11:06,440 --> 00:11:08,330
I’m not talking about Qingfeng.

149
00:11:08,330 --> 00:11:09,460
If not, who else is there?

150
00:11:09,460 --> 00:11:11,380
He Tianxing!

151
00:11:25,290 --> 00:11:28,090
What’s the relationship between you and He Tianxing?

152
00:11:41,350 --> 00:11:43,720
Actually,

153
00:11:45,910 --> 00:11:48,270
we don’t have much of a relationship.

154
00:11:50,980 --> 00:11:53,150
You like He Tianxing?

155
00:12:04,590 --> 00:12:08,340
It’s not really considered “liking.”

156
00:12:08,340 --> 00:12:10,920
This is a little complicated.

157
00:12:10,920 --> 00:12:17,030
I just respect, idolize, look up to, admire, and adore him.

158
00:12:20,950 --> 00:12:24,560
So you respect, idolise, look up to, admire, and adore

159
00:12:24,560 --> 00:12:27,620
a person who has no relationship with you?

160
00:12:31,770 --> 00:12:34,310
Everybody has an idol.

161
00:12:34,310 --> 00:12:37,080
I silently worship him in my heart.

162
00:12:37,080 --> 00:12:40,780
He is a very sacred symbol in my heart.

163
00:12:42,700 --> 00:12:44,400
Zheng Xiao’en.

164
00:12:45,590 --> 00:12:47,970
The question that I’m going to ask next...

165
00:12:47,970 --> 00:12:50,550
you must answer me seriously.

166
00:12:52,970 --> 00:12:57,860
The first time we met, you called me He Tianxing.

167
00:12:57,860 --> 00:13:02,960
After that, you kept mentioning that I look very similar to him.

168
00:13:06,610 --> 00:13:10,610
Zheng Xiao’en, look into my eyes.

169
00:13:12,580 --> 00:13:14,370
Tell me.

170
00:13:15,360 --> 00:13:18,150
Do you actually like me,

171
00:13:18,150 --> 00:13:20,460
or do you like that I look like him?

172
00:13:28,920 --> 00:13:30,770
Look at me!

173
00:13:36,710 --> 00:13:42,890
I'll need some time to answer this question.

174
00:13:44,150 --> 00:13:46,100
I have lots of time.

175
00:13:50,310 --> 00:13:52,660
Actually, I’m not too sure myself.

176
00:13:52,660 --> 00:13:55,390
At first, I thought Situ Aoran was equivalent to He Tianxing.

177
00:13:55,390 --> 00:13:58,610
After that, I felt that it was best if Situ Aoran wasn’t equivalent to He Tianxing.

178
00:13:58,610 --> 00:14:03,050
I hope that you can live happily and not become like He Tianxing.

179
00:14:06,510 --> 00:14:10,030
What if you can only choose one between the two of us?

180
00:14:19,610 --> 00:14:23,030
Can’t I choose both? Both of you are basically from different worlds.

181
00:14:23,030 --> 00:14:24,980
You can’t!

182
00:14:25,940 --> 00:14:28,300
He is him. I am me.

183
00:14:28,300 --> 00:14:30,200
Stop saying that I’m similar to He Tianxing.

184
00:14:30,200 --> 00:14:32,080
I am Situ Aoran!

185
00:14:32,080 --> 00:14:34,980
I’m not a substitute for anyone else.

186
00:14:34,980 --> 00:14:38,530
♫ Sleepwalking the whole world together ♫

187
00:14:38,530 --> 00:14:43,270
♫ How warm the sun is ♫

188
00:14:45,910 --> 00:14:48,700
♫ Feel it to your heart's content ♫

189
00:14:48,700 --> 00:14:52,660
♫ Got nothing but time ♫

190
00:14:52,660 --> 00:14:59,730
♫ I will accompany you in insomnia ♫

191
00:14:59,730 --> 00:15:06,360
♫ You don't need to face everything alone ♫

192
00:15:14,260 --> 00:15:16,200
Have you called the police?

193
00:15:17,270 --> 00:15:19,900
Why haven’t you called the police?

194
00:15:19,900 --> 00:15:23,210
Was it really the mafia’s doing, as reported in the magazine,

195
00:15:23,210 --> 00:15:25,320
and that’s why you don’t dare to call the police?

196
00:15:25,320 --> 00:15:29,160
Silly child, the He family has connections with both the police and the mafia.

197
00:15:29,160 --> 00:15:31,210
You don’t have to be scared.

198
00:15:31,210 --> 00:15:32,220
I’m not scared.

199
00:15:32,220 --> 00:15:33,660
Then call the police!

200
00:15:33,660 --> 00:15:35,550
I’ll call the police director-general now.

201
00:15:35,550 --> 00:15:37,630
You can’t.

202
00:15:37,630 --> 00:15:39,680
Why can’t I?

203
00:15:40,670 --> 00:15:45,250
Because... Because it’s... It’s...

204
00:15:45,250 --> 00:15:48,270
It was Sis who hit me.

205
00:15:48,270 --> 00:15:50,350
Has she gone crazy?

206
00:15:50,350 --> 00:15:52,420
He Mingli! Come out!

207
00:15:52,420 --> 00:15:54,320
Mom! Lower your volume.

208
00:15:54,320 --> 00:15:56,230
Sis is probably still sleeping.

209
00:15:56,820 --> 00:15:58,400
Just let her rest.

210
00:15:58,400 --> 00:16:01,710
I heard the doctor say that she has been very stressed recently.

211
00:16:01,710 --> 00:16:04,910
She takes a bunch of sleeping pills, but she still doesn’t sleep well.

212
00:16:04,910 --> 00:16:10,060
I was thinking, is it possible that her chronic insomnia is causing her to run amok?

213
00:16:10,730 --> 00:16:14,850
She always loses her temper for no reason. I think she’s ill.

214
00:16:14,850 --> 00:16:16,740
Mom, wait for me for a while.

215
00:16:18,270 --> 00:16:20,370
Why doesn't she try mine?

216
00:16:20,370 --> 00:16:23,120
This is also a sleeping pill. I think it's pretty effective.

217
00:16:23,120 --> 00:16:25,630
The important thing is that it's a small dosage and it's not addicting.

218
00:16:25,630 --> 00:16:28,730
Why don’t you give this to Sis to try next time?

219
00:16:28,730 --> 00:16:30,970
My baby, you are just so kind.

220
00:16:30,970 --> 00:16:32,850
You were beaten by your sister to this state,

221
00:16:32,850 --> 00:16:34,850
yet you still care about her.

222
00:16:34,850 --> 00:16:37,360
All right, I’ll give this to her to take.

223
00:16:37,360 --> 00:16:41,640
If she sleeps well, she won’t lose her temper all the time.

224
00:16:43,860 --> 00:16:47,490
I also don’t know why she became like this.

225
00:16:47,490 --> 00:16:51,180
Remember, if your sister hits you next time, you must dodge.

226
00:16:51,180 --> 00:16:53,620
- Don’t be so naive, okay?
- Okay.

227
00:16:53,620 --> 00:16:55,780
Mom will feel sorry for you.

228
00:16:59,270 --> 00:17:01,190
What?

229
00:17:01,190 --> 00:17:03,740
You gave the chairwoman pills to take?

230
00:17:03,740 --> 00:17:05,150
That’s right.

231
00:17:05,800 --> 00:17:07,530
Don’t worry.

232
00:17:07,530 --> 00:17:11,060
They’re just sleeping pills with a slightly more potent effect.

233
00:17:11,060 --> 00:17:14,770
At most, there will be some side effects.

234
00:17:17,160 --> 00:17:20,170
Not bad. You’ve improved very quickly.

235
00:17:20,170 --> 00:17:26,340
Now, just focus your attention on the board of directors.

236
00:17:26,340 --> 00:17:28,540
No problem.

237
00:17:28,540 --> 00:17:30,910
I’ve been ready for a long time.

238
00:17:38,170 --> 00:17:40,890
You can’t even set up meetings with a few directors?

239
00:17:40,890 --> 00:17:42,800
Are you rubbish?

240
00:17:42,800 --> 00:17:44,770
Continue making phone calls to them!

241
00:17:44,770 --> 00:17:47,330
If they still don’t answer, then send people to block them!

242
00:17:47,330 --> 00:17:49,950
This is such a simple task, yet I still have to teach you?

243
00:17:49,950 --> 00:17:51,630
Rubbish!

244
00:17:53,860 --> 00:17:58,710
Rubbish. Rubbish. Rubbish. Rubbish!

245
00:18:03,180 --> 00:18:04,730
You didn’t leave your room today.

246
00:18:04,730 --> 00:18:07,800
