In his eyes, I'm a goddamn loser who fails at everything he does!

504
00:45:16,720 --> 00:45:19,100
You just haven't succeeded yet.

505
00:45:19,100 --> 00:45:21,560
Haven't I been supporting you no matter what?

506
00:45:21,560 --> 00:45:24,570
Yeah, right.

507
00:45:24,570 --> 00:45:27,060
Thank you,

508
00:45:27,060 --> 00:45:29,520
but I hate you for that the most.

509
00:45:29,520 --> 00:45:33,760
Saint mode completely activated, supporting me no matter what.

510
00:45:33,760 --> 00:45:38,990
When you give me money, are you also laughing at me on the inside and looking down on me?

511
00:45:38,990 --> 00:45:40,930
This time, when I asked for NT$20,000,000 (~US$680,000),

512
00:45:40,930 --> 00:45:43,290
you didn't even blink, and you gave it to me.

513
00:45:43,290 --> 00:45:45,100
I know.

514
00:45:45,100 --> 00:45:49,000
Because you think this NT$20,000,000 will make me go away, and I won't disturb you.

515
00:45:49,000 --> 00:45:52,330
You think I don't know what you're thinking?

516
00:45:53,130 --> 00:45:54,510
I've never thought that before.

517
00:45:54,510 --> 00:45:56,900
You do think like that!

518
00:46:06,200 --> 00:46:10,030
Zheng Xiao'en! I'm going to count to three.

519
00:46:10,030 --> 00:46:15,190
If you don't come out, I won't even let you two be buried together!

520
00:46:15,190 --> 00:46:18,240
Xiao'en! Xiao'en!

521
00:46:18,240 --> 00:46:21,710
No matter if you're here or not, you're not allowed to come out!

522
00:46:21,710 --> 00:46:27,180
No matter what happens, cover your ears, close your eyes, and everything will be fine.

523
00:46:29,240 --> 00:46:30,920
One!

524
00:46:39,260 --> 00:46:41,420
Two!

525
00:46:41,420 --> 00:46:43,930
Zheng Xiao'en isn't even here!

526
00:46:43,930 --> 00:46:46,030
If there's anything, we can talk about it.

527
00:46:46,030 --> 00:46:47,990
It has nothing to do with Xiao'en.

528
00:46:49,610 --> 00:46:52,320
- Three!
- I'm right here.

529
00:46:56,230 --> 00:46:58,190
You're finally willing to come out?

530
00:46:58,190 --> 00:47:00,390
You really can tolerate it.

531
00:47:00,390 --> 00:47:03,810
Didn't I tell you not to come out no matter what? Hurry and leave!

532
00:47:03,810 --> 00:47:08,000
I said before that I won't leave you behind. I won't!

533
00:47:09,370 --> 00:47:12,730
So you intend on being an arsonist now?

534
00:47:12,730 --> 00:47:16,010
If I were your dad, I wouldn't want to give you any attention either.

535
00:47:16,010 --> 00:47:17,760
You only know how to feel sorry for yourself.

536
00:47:17,760 --> 00:47:19,700
How old are you? You're acting like a middle-schooler.

537
00:47:19,700 --> 00:47:22,350
It's about time you learn to take responsibility for your life.

538
00:47:24,480 --> 00:47:27,790
Brother, this is between us brothers.

539
00:47:27,790 --> 00:47:29,870
We can have a good chat.

540
00:47:29,870 --> 00:47:32,960
First let Xiao'en leave. Don't bring her into this.

541
00:47:32,960 --> 00:47:36,410
You really think I'm faking this?

542
00:47:36,410 --> 00:47:39,400
Do you believe that I'll burn you both until you're not even ashes?

543
00:47:39,400 --> 00:47:43,400
Situ Moran, if you dare to light the fire now,

544
00:47:43,400 --> 00:47:45,350
you definitely won't be able to get away with it.

545
00:47:45,350 --> 00:47:47,460
Don't force me.

546
00:47:47,460 --> 00:47:49,390
I'm warning you, don't force me.

547
00:47:49,390 --> 00:47:52,300
Do you really think doing this will make your dad love you?

548
00:47:53,880 --> 00:47:55,760
He won't!

549
00:47:55,760 --> 00:47:58,770
Even if Aoran dies, you're still you.

550
00:47:58,770 --> 00:48:01,580
You can never be Situ Aoran.

551
00:48:03,260 --> 00:48:05,080
Chuchu already called the police.

552
00:48:05,080 --> 00:48:07,840
The police are on the way.

553
00:48:07,840 --> 00:48:10,370
If you let us go now,

554
00:48:10,370 --> 00:48:13,180
I can tell them that you brothers had a small fight,

555
00:48:13,180 --> 00:48:15,820
and it was just a misunderstanding.

556
00:48:15,820 --> 00:48:19,080
If you really kill someone,

557
00:48:19,080 --> 00:48:21,960
the rest of your life will be ruined.

558
00:48:22,610 --> 00:48:26,290
If you're not spending the rest of your life in jail, then you're spending the rest of your life on the run.

559
00:48:26,290 --> 00:48:28,270
From then on, you won't be able to see the light.

560
00:48:28,270 --> 00:48:30,880
Is this what you want?

561
00:48:37,230 --> 00:48:39,260
You're so noisy.

562
00:48:39,970 --> 00:48:43,030
I'll take care of you first and then take care of Situ Aoran.

563
00:48:43,050 --> 00:48:45,960
Don't hurt her!

564
00:48:52,290 --> 00:48:54,100
Situ Moran!

565
00:48:57,900 --> 00:49:00,030
Aoran.

566
00:49:32,280 --> 00:49:36,800
You can't win against me, dear CEO brother.

567
00:49:39,990 --> 00:49:43,660
First, let Xiao'en go. I'll let you do whatever you want to me.

568
00:49:43,660 --> 00:49:45,870
No!

569
00:49:45,870 --> 00:49:48,530
Am I not the thorn in your side?

570
00:49:48,530 --> 00:49:53,060
If I just completely back down, would you be satisfied?

571
00:49:57,290 --> 00:50:01,190
Okay! Come here.

572
00:50:04,550 --> 00:50:06,230
Why are you switching with me?

573
00:50:06,230 --> 00:50:09,980
By doing this, everything we did before is worthless! Are you crazy?

574
00:50:11,360 --> 00:50:13,560
Just treat it as if I've gone crazy.

575
00:50:14,970 --> 00:50:18,070
For you, I'm willing.

576
00:50:32,130 --> 00:50:35,400
♫ My last wish is to never regret ♫

577
00:50:35,400 --> 00:50:41,530
♫ Brave out the heartbreak to no longer be afraid of heartbreaks ♫

