- You—
- I'm fine.

590
00:51:53,060 --> 00:51:54,980
What are you doing?

591
00:51:58,210 --> 00:51:59,820
Throw the knife away.

592
00:51:59,820 --> 00:52:03,090
If you dare to hurt him, I'll set it all on fire.

593
00:52:03,090 --> 00:52:06,230
Everyone dies and nobody lives.

594
00:52:07,050 --> 00:52:09,200
Zheng Xiao'en, stop it!

595
00:52:09,200 --> 00:52:11,260
Disappear before me right now. Hurry and leave!

596
00:52:11,260 --> 00:52:13,170
I don't want to. I won't leave!

597
00:52:13,170 --> 00:52:15,290
Is today the first day you met me? When have I ever been that obedient?

598
00:52:15,290 --> 00:52:18,070
Leave! Leave right now! Hurry and leave!

599
00:52:18,070 --> 00:52:20,120
You're almost dead, and you still care about whether I leave or not.

600
00:52:20,120 --> 00:52:23,090
You really think an overbearing CEO can conquer the universe?

601
00:52:23,090 --> 00:52:24,830
If you don't leave now, do you want to die?

602
00:52:24,830 --> 00:52:28,920
That's right. I want to die with you.

603
00:52:28,920 --> 00:52:32,610
If you die, how can I go on living peacefully?

604
00:52:32,610 --> 00:52:35,030
I can't do it.

605
00:52:35,030 --> 00:52:37,980
It's already like this and you're still arguing with me?

606
00:52:38,660 --> 00:52:40,400
Where did you come from?

607
00:52:40,400 --> 00:52:42,950
Why do I like a woman like you?

608
00:52:44,880 --> 00:52:47,090
You like me?

609
00:52:47,090 --> 00:52:49,030
No kidding!

610
00:52:51,260 --> 00:52:59,000
I never thought that I would personally hear you say that you like me.

611
00:53:02,460 --> 00:53:04,870
Are you two done?

612
00:53:11,750 --> 00:53:13,990
Even if I die now,

613
00:53:16,770 --> 00:53:18,300
I have no more regrets.

614
00:53:18,300 --> 00:53:21,740
No, I do.

615
00:53:23,870 --> 00:53:28,400
I still have a lot of things I want to do with you.

616
00:53:55,980 --> 00:53:58,420
- Xiao'en!
- Are you okay?

617
00:53:58,420 --> 00:54:00,810
Are you hurt anywhere?

618
00:54:00,810 --> 00:54:04,380
What about you? Does it hurt?

619
00:54:06,460 --> 00:54:10,580
Seeing that you're okay, any injuries no longer hurt.

620
00:54:50,470 --> 00:54:52,580
Does it hurt?

621
00:55:40,740 --> 00:55:42,910
What's wrong?

622
00:55:50,240 --> 00:55:52,910
I almost lost you.

623
00:56:16,880 --> 00:56:21,540
Your hand is still as warm as before.

624
00:56:27,980 --> 00:56:30,210
Remember what you promised me.

625
00:56:34,360 --> 00:56:36,460
As long as I reach out my hand,

626
00:56:36,460 --> 00:56:38,830
I will be able to touch you.

627
00:56:38,830 --> 00:56:41,970
This is the farthest distance you can be away from me.

628
00:56:46,120 --> 00:56:53,810
I can touch you, feel you, and sense you.

629
00:56:53,810 --> 00:57:01,920
From the beginning to the end, it's always been Situ Aoran, not anyone else.

630
00:57:07,230 --> 00:57:09,670
It's not He Tianxing.

631
00:57:11,310 --> 00:57:13,290
It's you.

632
00:57:15,980 --> 00:57:21,460
You're the one I like, Situ Aoran.

633
00:57:22,890 --> 00:57:25,920
You're no one's substitute.

634
00:57:26,670 --> 00:57:29,020
You're one of a kind.

635
00:57:30,570 --> 00:57:32,750
Nobody can replace you.

