I am He Mingli.

681
01:03:17,820 --> 01:03:20,040
Why am I here?

682
01:03:31,330 --> 01:03:33,790
Chairwoman, do you want to visit the psychiatrist?

683
01:03:33,790 --> 01:03:35,630
I can schedule you for a walk-in appointment right now.

684
01:03:35,630 --> 01:03:40,340
No, we can't let anyone know about this.

685
01:03:40,340 --> 01:03:42,160
Do you understand?

686
01:03:44,280 --> 01:03:46,570
Do you want to go out or did you just get back home?

687
01:03:46,570 --> 01:03:48,910
What did you do to be looking like this?

688
01:03:50,580 --> 01:03:55,960
I... suddenly had something urgent to attend to in the middle of the night.

689
01:04:08,910 --> 01:04:12,340
[Tianliang Group]

690
01:04:15,510 --> 01:04:17,780
- Good morning, everyone!
- Good morning, CHRO.

691
01:04:17,780 --> 01:04:20,790
- Good morning! Good morning!
- Good morning, CHRO.

692
01:04:20,790 --> 01:04:25,140
You dyed your hair! Looks good, looks good!

693
01:04:25,140 --> 01:04:27,960
Why are you here?

694
01:04:29,600 --> 01:04:32,060
Didn't you tell me to come back?

695
01:04:33,610 --> 01:04:35,990
- Me?
- Yeah.

696
01:04:35,990 --> 01:04:37,920
Yesterday you suddenly called me in the middle of the night

697
01:04:37,920 --> 01:04:41,060
to tell me to come back to work at the head office starting today. Did you forget?

698
01:04:41,060 --> 01:04:43,000
No way.

699
01:04:43,000 --> 01:04:45,010
Chairwoman.

700
01:04:45,860 --> 01:04:47,640
Tianjian is speaking the truth.

701
01:04:47,640 --> 01:04:52,040
Didn't you call me yesterday to tell me to let him come back?

702
01:04:56,510 --> 01:04:59,950
Sis, are you okay?

703
01:05:01,420 --> 01:05:05,000
How come your mental condition seems so bad?

704
01:05:05,000 --> 01:05:09,530
Did you forget everything you said last night?

705
01:05:09,530 --> 01:05:11,270
I—

706
01:05:12,460 --> 01:05:16,620
- What's going on?
- So strange.

707
01:05:16,620 --> 01:05:20,170
It's nothing. I didn't forget.

708
01:05:33,220 --> 01:05:35,640
Chairwoman, are you okay?

709
01:05:35,640 --> 01:05:40,250
Get out. I want some time alone for a bit.

710
01:05:40,250 --> 01:05:41,950
Okay.

711
01:05:57,330 --> 01:06:01,600
[Call records]
[Uncle Hu, Tianjian]

712
01:06:03,900 --> 01:06:06,030
There's no way.

713
01:06:06,030 --> 01:06:09,020
How come I have no memory of this at all?

714
01:06:13,830 --> 01:06:16,230
Come in.

715
01:06:16,230 --> 01:06:18,690
Chairwoman, bad news.

716
01:06:20,760 --> 01:06:22,900
Can't you just accept reality?

717
01:06:22,900 --> 01:06:26,530
You'll spend your life paving the way for me.

718
01:06:26,530 --> 01:06:29,000
It sounds kind of sad,

719
01:06:29,000 --> 01:06:34,110
but don't worry, I'll remember everything you've done for me.

720
01:06:34,110 --> 01:06:36,000
Once I officially take over,

721
01:06:36,000 --> 01:06:39,980
I absolutely won't mistreat a competent stepping stone such as yourself.

722
01:06:39,980 --> 01:06:41,670
He Tianjian!

723
01:06:41,670 --> 01:06:43,430
Turn it off!

724
01:06:43,430 --> 01:06:46,260
Turn all of it off!

725
01:07:11,240 --> 01:07:16,260
This is the calming cedar fragrance exclusive to the CEO's room.

726
01:07:16,910 --> 01:07:20,350
Never mind. I must be dreaming.

727
01:07:20,350 --> 01:07:22,960
I'll keep sleeping.

728
01:07:33,470 --> 01:07:36,320
It's not a dream! It's the CEO!

729
01:07:36,320 --> 01:07:39,660
So what should I do now?

730
01:07:39,660 --> 01:07:44,270
Should I pretend to sleep, or should I let the CEO pretend to sleep?

731
01:07:58,480 --> 01:08:00,350
Hey.

732
01:08:01,630 --> 01:08:05,750
Aoran. Situ Aoran!

733
01:08:05,750 --> 01:08:07,500
You—

734
01:08:08,680 --> 01:08:12,950
- Why didn't you save me?
- Huh?

735
01:08:16,660 --> 01:08:19,200
It's nothing.

736
01:08:19,200 --> 01:08:21,590
I'm awake now.

737
01:08:25,350 --> 01:08:31,130
Did you... have a nightmare?

738
01:08:37,250 --> 01:08:39,950
Does it have something to do with He Tianxing?

739
01:08:44,900 --> 01:08:47,590
What did you dream of?

740
01:08:52,260 --> 01:08:54,530
Me?

741
01:08:54,530 --> 01:08:57,260
I was in your dream?

742
01:08:59,510 --> 01:09:01,610
Like this.

743
01:09:06,860 --> 01:09:11,700
You could feel yourself grabbing my arm?

744
01:09:11,700 --> 01:09:14,910
But you actually did nothing to save me.

745
01:09:16,520 --> 01:09:19,790
Just like that, you let someone push me away.

746
01:09:20,590 --> 01:09:24,410
I didn't purposefully let go... it's—

747
01:09:29,200 --> 01:09:33,900
No matter what the circumstance is, you shouldn't let go of my hand.

748
01:09:55,590 --> 01:10:00,340
Then... what else did you dream of?

749
01:10:01,840 --> 01:10:05,020
I dreamt of... breakfast.

750
01:10:05,790 --> 01:10:09,810
I want to eat breakfast. Like how you used to make it.

751
01:10:29,190 --> 01:10:33,480
How could the woman that I, Situ Aoran, fall for be an ordinary woman?

752
01:10:33,480 --> 01:10:37,840
To me, you are the most special woman in the entire world.

753
01:10:37,840 --> 01:10:41,920
If only time could freeze at this very moment, that would be great.

754
01:10:41,920 --> 01:10:43,530
I know you like Zheng Xiao'en.

755
01:10:43,530 --> 01:10:46,400
Don't you want to know what place you have in Zheng Xiao'en's heart?

756
01:10:46,400 --> 01:10:48,430
Are you willing to lose her like this?

757
01:10:48,430 --> 01:10:53,670
Aoran still has dreams even now, so that means He Tianxing is still unconscious.

